                    &lt;img alt=&quot;下午察：宁王上市 香港重回金融中心宝座？&quot; title=&quot;下午察：宁王上市 香港重回金融中心宝座？&quot; src=&quot;https://cassette.sphdigital.com.sg/image/zaobao/38b10559d011586e12415040e1582f24b1b9772677041ce3c30df70c1cb77c80&quot; class=&quot;my-0 w-full rounded-[4px] object-contain&quot; referrerpolicy=&quot;no-referrer&quot;&gt;
